descript.abstract: This polygonal dataset consists of the 2000 Census County Boudaries for Arizona.
descript.purpose: The data are created to serve as base information for use in GIS systems for a variety of planning and analysis purposes. These data do not represent a legal record. Use of data for engineering work is prohibited.

procstep.procdesc:
The following ARC/INFO 8.1 commands were run to process the data downloaded from www.esri.com/data/download/census2000_tigerline/index.html
Ran SHAPEARC on the Census 2000 TIGER/Line shape files to create ARC/INFO coverages.
Ran PROJECT to change the source projection from Projection Geographic, units decimal degrees, Datum NAD83 to Projection UTM, zone 12, units meters, Datum NAD27.
Ran BUILD to update topology. Ran JOINITEM to join the demographic attributes to the PAT. Ran INDEX to increase selection speed.
